column4: Let me know if you need something from me
I'll be fixing up the freight interchanges soon
There is a gas station at 688,366 that could be started.
I'm going to build the oil net all integrated once I fix it in the north. I'll connect all of the southern gas stations using your player and leave the rest to you.
What is it that you want to hual from your sign at 163,215 ?
I'll be willing to transport it to the interchange
I just thought it would be easier to move by barge. But if you want to do it, feel free
I will also need sand from 180, 363 and 188, 373, but not for at least a day or two...
I'll the lines in place, ready to go by then.
You will just hook into SPax to get there?
